examples.en: Nothing's settled yet.
It was his settled purpose.
He finally settled down.
Snow settled on the roofs.
His gaze settled on her face.
examples.ru: Его взгляд остановился на её лице.

examples.en: Dust had settled on everything.
A cough settled in her chest.
examples.ru: Кашель обосновался в её груди. / В её груди поселился кашель.

examples.en: I still don't feel settled in my job.
examples.ru: Я всё ещё не освоился на работе.

examples.en: I'm delighted that we have settled the matter.
examples.ru: Я рад, что мы уладили дело.

examples.en: I wish this were a settled question.
examples.ru: Как ни жаль, этот вопрос ещё не решён.

examples.en: The immigrants settled in the Midwest.
An uneasy silence settled over the room.
At last all the excitement had settled down.
Two birds settled on the fence.
We finally settled the argument.
Several points remain to be settled.
A nurse settled the old man into a chair.
examples.ru: Медсестра усадила пожилого мужчину в кресло.

examples.en: Isn't it time you settled to work on your paper?
examples.ru: Тебе не пора сесть за твою письменную работу?

examples.en: When we've settled in properly, we'll invite all our friends.
examples.ru: Как только как следует обустроимся, то пригласим всех наших друзей.

examples.en: We settled for a lower price.
examples.ru: Мы согласились на более низкую цену.

examples.en: Storm clouds settled darkly over the town.
Tom picked himself up and settled on his bench again
examples.ru: Том поднялся и снова сел на скамью

examples.en: Good, that's settled then. We'll all meet here next Wednesday.
examples.ru: Хорошо, тогда договорились: мы все встречаемся здесь в следующую среду.

examples.en: Don't you ever get mad, I'm gonna have everything settled down.
examples.ru: Не злись ты так, я всё улажу.

examples.en: She settled the teacart.
The wind settled in the West.
The two parties finally settled.
The Swedes settled in Minnesota.
This land was settled by Germans.
He settled the farm 200 years ago.
